{
  "$comment": [
    "Per-game boss catalogs for DSDeathOverlay.",
    "",
    "Each entry's 'gameId' matches the 'shortTag' in games.json (DSR/DS2/DS3/SEK).",
    "Bosses are keyed by a stable 'id' (lower-case, dash-separated) used for persistence",
    "and shown by 'name'. Detection defaults to 'manual': press F11 (or click in edit",
    "mode) to mark the active boss; the next death increments that boss's counter.",
    "",
    "To wire automatic detection in the future, set Detection.Type to 'pointerChainFlag',",
    "provide a chainOffsets64 (or chainOffsets32) that yields an integer boss flag at the",
    "end of the walk, and add 'flagToBossId' mapping each integer value to a boss id.",
    "The reserved value 0 means 'no active boss'. The shipped catalogs use manual mode;",
    "community-supplied offsets can be dropped in via this file without rebuilding."
  ],
